public boolean authenticate(java.lang.String a_user_id,
                            java.lang.String a_password)
Preconditions:
  • There is a list of users and passwords associated with them.
Postconditions:
  • Delivers enabled or disabled access upon authentication

Parameters:
a_user_id - the user's ID
a_password - The password correlated with the user's ID
Returns:
True if the password matches ID, false if otherwise

gatherFeedback

public void gatherFeedback(Schedule the_schedule)
Gathers feedback by processing the schedule by iterating over the UserCommunity's list of students. The feedback is then stored and ready to be returned when prompted.

Preconditions:
  • The schedule has been processed and is nonnull
Postconditions:
  • Internal data representations of feedback ready to be prompted for.

Parameters:
the_schedule - The schedule to be processed.
